{
  "name": "z-nomp",
  "version": "0.0.4",
  "description": "Bitcoin Gold (Equihash) stratum mining pool based on NOMP",
  "keywords": [
    "stratum",
    "mining",
    "pool",
    "server",
    "poolserver",
    "zclassic",
    "zcash",
    "equihash"
  ],
  "homepage": "https://github.com/zencashio/z-nomp",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/zencashio/z-nomp/issues"
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "author": "Joshua Yabut",
  "contributors": [
    "aayanl",
    "sennevb",
    "Matthew Little",
    "vekexasia",
    "TheSeven"
  ],
  "main": "init.js",
  "bin": {
    "block-notify": "./scripts/blockNotify.js"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/zencashio/z-nomp.git"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "async": "^2.5.0",
    "bignum": "^0.12.5",
    "body-parser": "^1.18.2",
    "colors": "^1.1.2",
    "compression": "^1.7.1",
    "dateformat": "^2.2.0",
    "dot": "^1.1.2",
    "equihashjs-verify": "^1.0.5",
    "express": "^4.16.2",
    "extend": "^3.0.1",
    "mysql": "^2.15.0",
    "node-json-minify": "^1.0.0",
    "node-watch": "^0.5.5",
    "nonce": "^1.0.4",
    "redis": "^2.8.0",
    "request": "^2.83.0",
    "stratum-pool": "git+https://github.com/SpiritedAwayLab/node-stratum-pool-btg.git"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=0.10"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "start": "LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$PWD/node_modules/stratum-pool/node_modules/equihashverify/build/Release/:$PWD/node_modules/equihashverify/build/Release/ node init.js"
  }
}
